dc_title_s: Essex County, New Jersey highways - south half
dc_description_s: Southern half of a base map of Essex County prepared by the New Jersey Stte Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. Extensive legend indicates road system designations and road types, railroads and railroad crossings, waterways and drainage, boundries, bridges and tunnels, and general culture features.
